# The FastAPI web backend (app.py) needs no environment variables — it only
# extracts text from uploaded bills. The AI analysis runs client-side in the
# browser using the user's own Anthropic API key (never touches the server).
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY below is only needed if you run mcp_server.py locally
# for testing (Mode 2). When added to Claude Desktop/Code it's usually set
# via the MCP server's own env config instead of this file.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key
